== Exercise: Write SWTBot test

=== Installation
		
			Ensure to install SWTBot into your Eclipse IDE. See
			<xref linkend="swtbotinstallation" />
			for detailed information.
		
	

=== Create project
		
			Create a new plug-in
			called
			_com.example.e4.rcp.todo.uitest_
			and add the following dependencies to the
			_MANIFEST.MF_
			file:

			<itemizedlist>
				<listitem>
					org.eclipse.swt
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					org.junit
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					org.eclipse.swtbot.go
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					org.eclipse.swtbot.junit4_x
				</listitem>
				<listitem>
					org.eclipse.swtbot.swt.finder
				</listitem>
			</itemizedlist>
		
	

